title: (digimob) Occult Mob's Submissions Digest #23.2
description:
Occult.digital.mobilization (Digimob) brings you another submissions digest with content not included in our mega-torrents.

This torrent represents a work of LOVE. All texts so far gathered, as well as all future gatherings, aim to facilitate the studies of sincere students.

Future releases will include submissions from users like YOU.

Digimob&#039;s archive provides an invaluable service to dedicated students of the occult sciences, and a forum community has been created to provide a platform for these students to engage in respectful discourse on topics related to our releases. Digimob invites you to join our new forum community at http://digimob.tk.

For some of us, the time has come to mobilize. If you have an interest in assisting in this process - we all have strengths to bring to the table - please email occult.digital.mobilization @ gmail . com. What are you waiting for?


Notable submissions in this digest include:
Idries Shah - "Oriental Magic" & "The Sufis"
Allan Leo - "Astrology for All" & "The Progressed Horoscope"
Robert Ambelain
Aleister Crowley, OTO rituals & sex magick
Bill Heidrick
Dionysus the Areopagite
Enochian Magick
Kabbalah
Gareth Knight
Jason Augustus Newcomb
The Oss Films
C.S. Hyatt
